<TYPE>
<P>
Column; Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA110894-0140 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 096503 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 8, 1994, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
