</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Alemany High's Samantha Rigley, the Times All-Valley girls basketball player 
of the year in 1994, said Monday she will sign a letter of intent to play 
basketball at Pepperdine. 
</P>
<P>
 The NCAA's weeklong fall signing period begins Wednesday. She considered the 
