 Siemens Unveils Ties With U.S. Firms: The company announced an alliance with 
Scientific Atlanta Inc. and Sun Microsystems Inc. to develop and market systems 
to transmit multimedia services worldwide.The alliance centers on "IMMXpress" 
systems that deliver data and sound and video products through cable and 
