By Jack Searles 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Gorilla Foods, an Ojai producer of wheat protein-based meat substitutes, has 
signed a letter of intent to be acquired by Wholesome and Hearty Foods Inc. of 
Portland, Ore. 
</P>
<P>
 Under the agreement, a group of executives headed by Michael Meek, president 
