60.2% VOTER TURNOUT IS PREDICTED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Today is Election Day. The polls are open from 7 a.m. until 8 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 * TURNOUT: Officials forecast that 60.2% of the state's registered voters will 
cast ballots -- about 8.8 million votes. 
</P>
<P>
 * ON THE BALLOT: Governor, U.S. senator and other statewide offices, seats in 
the House of Representatives, state legislative seats, 10 statewide ballot 
measures and local offices. 
</P>
<P>
 * WEATHER: Fair, with highs in the mid-60s to the low 70s. 
</P>
